    {
      "chinese": "夜深了，外面一點聲音都沒有，打開窗戶，遙望在遠處的天空裡，看到繁星以及一顆大的月亮，照亮在山林的部落及外面的都市，無論走在部落或都市，應該都非常平順。",
      "ab": "cakan bangi’ la, ungat bangbanglit, gumawah garasu’, tuskaw kaṟal bawi’. payux ka hangitux lu sabutingan ci yaba ka buṟating, pascex ci alang lu alang banux, ana maskakiy tu’uy nanahi’ lu alang banux, as rilot matox kora’ ka tu’uy.",
